article:
This is a list of station locations used by Amtrak in order by station name.
Each station is also identified by a three-letter code. These codes are not the
same as the list of IATA-indexed train stations or the three character IATA
airport codes.

Note that this list is in order by station name, there is also a list in order
by Amtrak station code. The cities listed in the list below are links to the
actual cities indicated and not to pages dealing with the station itself; pages
related to the actual station appear on the right side of the station code. All
stations are in the United States unless otherwise indicated. Â 




*any stop en route, not otherwise specified (ENP)
categories: Railway stations in the United States
